OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772482267
OL,3,C'Wrong call to join Iran war': O'Neill
OL,4,Chits out at UK Iran response
OL,6,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill has
OL,7,Fdefended her non-attendance at high-
OL,8,Flevel security briefings on the US-
OL,9,FIsraeli attacks on Iran saying it is
OL,10,Fis "absolutely the wrong call" for the
OL,11,FUK to "join in this war".
OL,13,FShe did not attend Saturday's meeting
OL,14,Fand has again refused to attend
OL,15,Fanother on Monday.
OL,26,@rD@DOUrD@^O]sD@GOUsD@XO]
