OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772482267
OL,3,C'Wrong call to join Iran war': O'Neill
OL,4,Chits out at UK Iran response
OL,6,FDeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,7,FPengelly, who attended the weekend
OL,8,Fmeeting and is at Monday's, said she
OL,9,Fwas told there are "many, many
OL,10,Fthousands of people" from Northern
OL,11,FIreland in countries targeted by Iran.
OL,13,FIran and Iranian-backed militias have
OL,14,Ffired missiles at Israel and Arab
OL,15,Fstates, while Israel and the US
OL,16,Fpounded targets in Iran as the war in
OL,17,Fthe Middle East expanded.
OL,26,@qD@TOUrD@TO]
