OL,3,C'Wrong call to join Iran war': O'Neill
OL,4,Chits out at UK Iran response
OL,6,FCyprus said a drone attack targeted a
OL,7,FBritish base, RAF Akrotiri, hours
OL,8,Fafter Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,9,Fannounced that American forces would
OL,10,Fbe allowed to use British bases to
OL,11,Fstrike Iranian missile sites.
OL,13,FAbout 300,000 Britons are believed to
OL,14,Fbe in countries targeted by Iran, and
OL,15,F102,000 are registered with the
OL,16,FForeign Office for updates as
OL,17,Fofficials examine all options,
OL,18,Fincluding a potential mass evacuation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
