PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772482267
OL,3,C'Wrong call to join Iran war': O'Neill
OL,4,Chits out at UK Iran response
OL,6,FAsked about her decision not to attend
OL,7,Fthe briefing at the weekend with her
OL,8,FExecutive counterpart and the leaders
OL,9,Fof the Scottish and Welsh devolved
OL,10,Fnations, Ms O'Neill said she has
OL,11,Fengaged with the UK and Irish
OL,12,FGovernments and her first priority
OL,13,Fremains seeing those travelling or
OL,14,Fworking in the region "extracted from
OL,15,Fwhat is potentially a very dangerous
OL,16,Fand catastrophic situation".
OL,26,@vD@WOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
