PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772482267
OL,3,C'Wrong call to join Iran war': O'Neill
OL,4,Chits out at UK Iran response
OL,6,FShe told reporters at Stormont: "We
OL,7,Fall know actually many people that are
OL,8,Fthere and we all know that people are
OL,9,Freally, really worried, families are
OL,10,Freally, really anxious.
OL,12,F"Our job is to try to remain engaged
OL,13,Fand to get those people safely
OL,14,Fextracted. But I fundamentally
OL,15,Fdisagree with the fact that the war
OL,16,Fhas begun, and I fundamentally
OL,17,Fdisagree with the British Government's
OL,18,Fapproach."
OL,26,@nD@aOUtD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
