FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772482267
OL,3,C'Wrong call to join Iran war': O'Neill
OL,4,Chits out at UK Iran response
OL,6,FShe earlier said: "I think this is a
OL,7,Freckless war. This is a war that
OL,8,Fshould never have begun.
OL,10,F"Where is this all going to end?
OL,11,FBecause over the course of the last 48
OL,12,Fhours things are really spiralling out
OL,13,Fof control.
OL,15,F"We see more and more countries are
OL,16,Fnow engaged in this war. This is
OL,17,Fdeath, this is destruction. This is
OL,18,Fnot going to bring about a peaceful
OL,19,Foutcome.
OL,26,@nD@SOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
