PN,44507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772482267
OL,3,C'Wrong call to join Iran war': O'Neill
OL,4,Chits out at UK Iran response
OL,6,F"What we need to see is dialogue, what
OL,7,Fwe need to see is adherence to
OL,8,Finternational law, what we need to see
OL,9,Fis conversation that actually brings
OL,10,Fthis to an end and allows people to
OL,11,Fsafely get on with their lives.
OL,13,FMs O'Neill described the Iranian
OL,14,Fregime as "brutal", "repressive" and
OL,15,Fone that "failed to live up to human
OL,16,Frights standards", but "it's not for
OL,17,Finternational committee to come in,
OL,18,Fbreach international law, throw out
OL,19,Fthe rules of diplomacy, and actually
OL,20,Fhave us in a situation where today
OL,21,Flives are being lost hour after hour."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@KOUvD@RO]vD@UOUvD@`O]wD@JOUxD@
OL,26,AQO]xD@XOU}D@fO]
