OL,3,C'Wrong call to join Iran war': O'Neill
OL,4,Chits out at UK Iran response
OL,6,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson said the
OL,7,FIranian regime "has had very strong
OL,8,Fconnections with terrorists who tried
OL,9,Fto destroy Northern Ireland", and
OL,10,FIranian people now have the
OL,11,Fopportunity "to pursue democracy for
OL,12,Ftheir own benefit and nobody else's".
OL,14,F"I shed no tears for the ayatollah,
OL,15,Fand I won't concern myself about
OL,16,Fwhether individuals want to argue the
OL,17,Ftoss about whether the intervention of
OL,18,Fthe weekend was legal or not," he said.
OL,26,@oD@POUqD@\O]sD@MOUtD@dO]vD@AOUzD@^O]
