OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772482267
OL,3,C'Wrong call to join Iran war': O'Neill
OL,4,Chits out at UK Iran response
OL,6,FAsked if he supported the UK
OL,7,FGovernment's involvement he said: "I
OL,8,Fthink it is a matter of fact that we
OL,9,Fare involved. I think we should have
OL,10,Fbeen involved earlier. At least we
OL,11,Fshouldn't have denied the use of our
OL,12,FRAF bases."
